# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Go build artifacts
#
# NOTE: the shipped plugin binary `gorpc/stash-auto-vision-tagging-rpc` is
# tracked deliberately — Stash loads it directly and users are not expected
# to build from source unless they're cross-compiling. The patterns below
# cover incidental build output only; they do not match the committed
# binary because it has no `.exe` / `.test` / `.out` suffix.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test
*.out
gorpc/vendor/

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Logs / scratch
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
*.tmp
tmp/
scratch/
